originalText.text:
Most dishonest and unpleasant staff I have ever had to deal with. Things started going sideways a few months ago when they just forgot to renew my prescription. My doctor stopped sending them my prescription a couple of months ago, and yet they keep showing up at my door with meds (from an expired/outdated prescription) anyway, not even caring the dosage may be off. Extremely unprofessional. It also looks like they have been charging my insurance for meds I either only partially got or not even at all. In some places, this would be called fraud, but I guess not in NY?
Please stay as far away from them as you can.
